cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use RIV-Bench, please cite it as below."
title: "RIV-Bench: Remediation Intent Verification Benchmark"
abstract: >-
  A reproducible benchmark for verifying whether an automated infrastructure-as-code
  remediation satisfies a compliance control's intent rather than merely passing a
  syntactic linter, with a labeled fixture set across openly available frameworks
  (CIS AWS/Azure/GCP, SOC 2) and a naive baseline that exposes the silent
  lint-pass-but-intent-unmet failure class.
type: dataset
authors:
